      "id": "scenario_2a3_s1",
      "name": "Start the Motor-Pump",
      "description": "The motor isolator SW_Iso is open. The suction and discharge valves are already open. Close SW_Iso to energise M1 — the motor drives the shaft, which automatically starts pump P1. The pump has no separate start button; the motor IS the control.",
